snippet.title: Magic Star: a New Music Dance Journey
snippet.description:
Magic Star is a music game which includes Karaoke, dancing, socializing, and role developing. Players can experience all kinds of new and interesting music rhythm game play , You can also collect various of luxury outfits and items in different styles，build a lovely home with your love . Combined with video, voice, bullet screen, LBS and other social interaction, you will experience a new virtual world of music.
